<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/148033-so-who-killed-robin">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[So who killed Robin?!?!? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
