<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/148033-so-who-killed-robin">7 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/148033-so-who-killed-robin">See all 7 answers</a>
</li>
