<div id="review_1962578" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1962578" />
    <a title="Allison" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/30019-allison"><img alt="Allison" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1479137463p2/30019.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1962578?book_show_action=true">Jun 14, 2007</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Allison" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Allison" href="/user/show/30019-allison">Allison</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30019-allison?shelf=fiction">fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30019-allison?shelf=never-finished">never-finished</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1962578" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14702052996513879036">I LOVED The Secret History. I do not love this. Elegant prose can only keep a reader for so long. I imagine that many people, me included, do not want a 10 page description of two troubled twentysomething doing crystal meth and getting sunburnt in the middle of July. I actually made the 200 page mark. With the potential of more sweaty boys on drugs in the next 400 pages, I put the book down and re-read The Secret History instead.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


