        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer701116712" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15618924467359411652">This was far too big a book for this story. Just loads of unnecessary description and background about certain things. It was very slow but i still enjoyed the story. I would read another book by Donna Tartt as I&apos;ve heard the others are far superior to this. </span>
  <span id="freeText15618924467359411652" style="display:none">This was far too big a book for this story. Just loads of unnecessary description and background about certain things. It was very slow but i still enjoyed the story. I would read another book by Donna Tartt as I've heard the others are far superior to this. </span>
